M106 S0
M106 P2 S0
;TYPE:Custom
M117
M83 ;relative extrusion
M104 S141 ;Preheat Nozzle to z-probe-temp and do NOT wait (M109 = preheat and wait)
M140 S55
G4 P1000 ;preheat bed 3 minutes if bed temp is higher than 80 degree (S1 bed will bend while preheating very hot and thus give false z offset values)

G28 X Y ;home only X Y (while preheating)

G1 Y250 F6000 
G1 X47 F6000 		;Park Bin Position
G1 Y270  F6000		;Park Bin Position

M109 S181 ;wait for extruder temperature
G1 E-3 F3000 ;retract a bit
; Erster Wipe
M104 S200; start heating up hotend to final temperature and continue
M140 S55; change setpoint of the heatbed to final temperature and continue
;G1 X0 F6000
G1 Y250
G1 X84 ;wipe position left x
G1 Y270 ;wipe and park position y
G1 X98 ;wipe to the right
G1 X84 ;wipe to the left

:complex wipe
G1 Y264
G1 X98 Y275
G1 X84 Y264
G1 X98 Y264
G1 X84 Y275
G1 X81


; Park Position
G1 Y250
G1 X47 F6000 		;Park Bin Position
G1 Y270  F6000		;Park Bin Position

; Zweiter Wipe
M109 S200 ; wait for hotend final temperature
M104 S141 ; Start cooldown
M106 S255 ;fan on for Park on Rubber already(off=M107), we will wipe while the nozzle already is cooling down 
;G1 E-3 F3000 ;retract a bit
;G1 X0 F6000
G1 Y250
G1 X84 ;wipe position left x
